dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.phy.hw.PPortAspectCompoundResourceDetails
dataStructure.description:
This class is a concrete class that defines the semantics of the PhysicalPortsInResourcePort aggregation. For example, it will describe characteristics and behavior of the PhysicalPorts that make up this particular ResourcePort in terms of dependencies and how a PhysicalPort interacts with other PhysicalPorts.

This association class is optional
dataStructure.label: PPortAspectCompoundResourceDetails
